The paper focuses on using deep learning models to detect code smells in software, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The use of deep learning also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The specific programming language used (C#) suggests a focus on programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the use of transfer learning suggests a focus on neural networks (cs.NE).
